Week 4: Final Insights and Report

In Week 4, I reviewed my dashboard and tried to understand the sales data better.

Key Insights:
- Technology category has the highest sales compared to other categories
- Sales change over time and show a clear trend
- West region has higher sales compared to other regions
- Some products are selling more than others

Business Suggestions:
- Focus more on high-performing categories like Technology
- Try to improve sales in regions where performance is low
- Promote top-selling products to increase overall revenue
- Regularly check sales trends to make better business decisions

Conclusion:
This project helped me understand how to analyze sales data using Excel, SQL and Power BI.
